<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. Male genitalia (ventral view) and terminalia (dorsal view) of Sinomiopteryx spp. A-C S. guangxiensis Wang & Bi, 1991 (IEGU: HASG 1) D-F S. sp. 1 (IEGU: HASSP 1 - 1) G-I S. sp. 2 (IEGU: HASSP 2 - 1). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 10. Holotypes of Arriini spp. A, E, I, M dorsal habitus B, F, J, N ventral habitus C, G, K, O lateral habitus D, H, L, P labels A-D A. brevifrons comb. nov. (SEM) E-H A. leigongshanensis (IEGU) I-L A. pallida (NFU) M-P S. guangxiensis (SEM). Not to scale." , "Figure 4. Male genitalia (ventral view) and terminalia (dorsal view) of Arria spp. A-C A. pura sp. nov., holotype D-F A. leigongshanensis (Ge & Chen, 2008), holotype G-I A. pallida (Zhang, 1987) (IEGU: HAAP 1) J-L A. sp. 2 (IEGU: HAASP 2 - 1). Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/521316" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/521321" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/521315" .

